#rad
       cot(α+2kπ)=cot α
               |    π
cot(π-α)=-cot α|cot(-- +α)=-tan α
               |    2
---------------|-------------------
               |    π
 cot(π+α)=cot α|cot(-- -α)=tan α
               |    2
#deg
        cot(α+k*360°)=cot α
cot(180°-α)=-cot α|cot(90°+α)=-tan α
------------------|-------------------
 cot(180°+α)=cot α|cot(90°-α)=tan α